OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1783521451
OL,3,CFamily of boy injured in hit-and-run
OL,4,Cmake plea for information
OL,6,FThe family of a four-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fwas seriously injured in a hit-and-run
OL,8,Fin South Shields have appealed to
OL,9,Fanyone with information to come
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police received a report
OL,13,Fthat a motorcycle had collided with a
OL,14,Fmother and child as they crossed the
OL,15,Froad outside Ocean Beach Pleasure
OL,16,FPark, on the seafront, shortly before
OL,17,F3.30pm on Saturday (27 June).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
