OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1783521451
OL,3,CFamily of boy injured in hit-and-run
OL,4,Cmake plea for information
OL,6,FThe motorcycle ` described as a petrol-
OL,7,Fpowered motorbike intended for road
OL,8,Fuse but not displaying a registration
OL,9,Fplate ` was then reported to have left
OL,10,Fthe scene towards the Westoe Road area
OL,11,Fof the town, police said.
OL,13,FThe boy sustained serious injuries and
OL,14,Fwas taken to hospital, where he
OL,15,Fremains. The woman, aged in her 30s,
OL,16,Fsustained minor injuries and was also
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1783521451
OL,3,CFamily of boy injured in hit-and-run
OL,4,Cmake plea for information
OL,6,FSpeaking following the incident, the
OL,7,Ffamily said: "We had been enjoying a
OL,8,Flovely summer's day out at the
OL,9,Fseafront.
OL,11,F"After enjoying our fish and chips, we
OL,12,Fbegan to cross the road towards South
OL,13,FMarine Park to buy an ice cream.
OL,15,F"As we crossed the road towards the
OL,16,Fpedestrian island, the rider collided
OL,17,Fwith us and then failed to stop.
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1783521451
OL,3,CFamily of boy injured in hit-and-run
OL,4,Cmake plea for information
OL,6,F"We are urging anyone who saw anything
OL,7,For knows who this person is `
OL,8,Fincluding the rider himself ` to come
OL,9,Fforward."
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police have also released
OL,12,Fan image of a motorcyclist they would
OL,13,Flike to speak to in connection with
OL,14,Fthe incident.
OL,16,FThe force said its roads policing unit
OL,17,Fhave carried out a number of
OL,18,Fenquiries, including a recent review
OL,19,Fof CCTV footage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]
